{"word":"φρύαγμα","slug":"φρύαγμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φρύαγμα</b></el> <el>(φρύαγμα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φρυάσσομαι'><el>φρυάσσομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a violent snorting, neighing</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>wanton behaviour, insolence</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}